{"tid":1590261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候幫自己選區開始選舉工程","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T18:19:59.000Z","uid":93479,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82678dc8fe21d45af9e3f53ecafd2d8336964f71","tid":1590261,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"鼓舞一下大家先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>十一月一定贏</strong></span></span> (除非政府DQ晒反對派，或者直頭種票箱入票站)<br />\n<br />\n問題係點樣將現在九月嘅火帶去十一月？<br />\n<br />\n儘早開始選舉工程，將現有捐助的資源轉為大規模捐助全港黃絲候選人<br />\n<br />\n有助將大眾已經疲累的焦點轉移返自己熟悉和關心的居住社區，但勇武撚狗仍繼續，並繼續攻向新屋嶺集中營<br />\n<br />\n我唔熟選舉例<br />\n有無一啲有公信力團體搞眾籌？合唔合法？<br />\n<br />\n因為我知有啲黃候選人想打屋邨鐵票倉，但資源有到係好唔夠........."},{"pid":"b2da0419028eb4b6bce4cfd0d08a9739de0bad88","tid":1590261,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"1de7b355e6da285cf8d1fbc43188989abfa1e204","tid":1590261,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79f595db2f29aa0ff49e9d1b07f5fc619499b700","tid":1590261,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec7a4001fb0b898228f13a1606fe0bce7904fceb","tid":1590261,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79f595db2f29aa0ff49e9d1b07f5fc619499b700","tid":1590261,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除